I don't think it's funny. I think it's sad.

40:30.887 --> 40:34.181
There's lonely people. It's just not me.

40:34.349 --> 40:39.061
You know, if you want my opinion,
it's this ad or persona or whatever.

40:39.229 --> 40:41.688
Big Donnie? Are you out of your mind?

40:41.856 --> 40:44.608
What kind of clients did you think
you were gonna attract?

40:44.776 --> 40:45.984
Did I ask your opinion?

40:46.152 --> 40:48.403
I'm just saying
you need to sell yourself better.

40:48.571 --> 40:50.489
And then you can get into a situation...

40:50.657 --> 40:53.075
...where you feel more confident
and more protected.

40:53.243 --> 40:56.745
And frankly, you need to add a photo.

40:56.913 --> 40:59.373
I did that. Online.

40:59.541 --> 41:01.542
Of your face.

41:01.709 --> 41:05.879
Are you fucking kidding me?
Tanya, I'm a highly respected educator.

41:06.047 --> 41:07.631
Nobody can know who I am.

41:07.799 --> 41:10.717
Ray, you missed the class
in creative marketing.

41:11.136 --> 41:14.221
There are so many different ways
you can sell yourself.

41:14.389 --> 41:16.974
Look, if you want, I can help.

41:17.142 --> 41:19.601
I mean, when I'm not working
on lyric bread.

41:19.853 --> 41:21.228
[SCOFFS]

41:21.604 --> 41:23.564
You wanna help me sell myself?

41:23.940 --> 41:27.109
Yeah. I mean, not for free.

41:27.277 --> 41:31.989
Maybe for like a percentage
of some kind.

41:35.285 --> 41:37.286
You wanna be my pimp.

41:39.247 --> 41:40.789
Yeah.

42:10.028 --> 42:11.445
RAY:
Hey, Damon.

42:12.280 --> 42:13.447
Damon!

42:15.700 --> 42:16.742
Dad?

42:18.453 --> 42:20.412
Hold on real quick.

42:21.372 --> 42:22.915
Dad, what are you doing here?

42:23.082 --> 42:24.791
Just... Just saying hi.

42:24.959 --> 42:26.960
Looks like you got a pretty good spot.

42:27.128 --> 42:30.005
Been camping all night, huh? Wow.

42:30.173 --> 42:31.215
Yeah.

42:31.841 --> 42:33.508
Hey...

42:34.385 --> 42:38.305
...I thought this might come in handy.

42:40.433 --> 42:43.727
Oh, no, no, Dad. It's fine.
Ronnie already gave me everything I needed.

42:44.229 --> 42:47.814
Look, you spend Ronnie's money
on something else, okay?

42:47.982 --> 42:49.816
This is for Godhead.

43:10.797 --> 43:16.009
RAY: You know, it might seem strange,
but for the first time in years...

43:16.302 --> 43:18.762
...I felt pretty good.
